- `ws_client::tests::connect_tls` - Connect with TLS (wss://)
- `ws_client::tests::connect_with_headers` - Custom headers in handshake
- `ws_client::tests::connect_subprotocol` - Subprotocol negotiation
- `ws_client::tests::send_text` - Send text message
